MIRAE

未来 / 미래
The future of streaming.



WHAT IS MIRAE?

Mirae is a modern Korean drama streaming platform built with:

- SvelteKit
- Bun
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS

Focused on speed, immersion, and cinematic browsing,
Mirae delivers a smooth OTT-style experience inspired by modern streaming platforms.



FEATURES

- cinematic homepage
- responsive streaming UI
- dynamic hero banners
- TMDB powered discovery
- hover preview effects
- personalized recommendations
- continue watching
- watchlist system
- smooth transitions
- mobile-first design
- fast navigation
- dark UI aesthetics



TECH STACK

Frontend
- SvelteKit
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS

Runtime
- Bun

APIs
- TMDB API
- YouTube trailers

Architecture
- component-based structure
- lazy-loaded media
- optimized routing
- edge-ready deployment



PROJECT STRUCTURE

src/
├── lib/
├── routes/
├── components/
├── stores/
├── styles/
└── utils/



DEVELOPMENT

Install dependencies:

bun install

Run development server:

bun run dev



BUILD

Create production build:

bun run build



DESIGN PHILOSOPHY

Mirae is built around three ideas:

- speed
- simplicity
- immersion

Minimal UI noise.
Fast interactions.
Cinematic presentation.



